title: Exception throw when exporting data from a table containing highlight/map
description: Description: Exception throws when exporting data from the attached report.
OB: When attempting to export data from a table containing highlight/map, an exception is thrown in the ReportEngineService.getMetaData() method.
EB: When exporting the data in the table, the expected result is that the data should be exported without any exceptions.
SR:
To reproduce this issue, follow these steps:
1. Open the attached report.
2. Attempt to export data from a table containing highlight/map.
3. Observe the exception being thrown.
